**Answer:**  
Additionally, you can obtain a list of poses for the reef poles (or your positions needed to score on each reef pole) by applying two transformations to each AprilTag—one for the left and one for the right. Then utilize the nearest method as previously.

We implement this as follows:  
```java  
for (Pose2d pose : tagPoses) {  
    reefPoleLocations.add(pose.transformBy(APRILTAG_LEFT_TRANSFORM));  
    reefPoleLocations.add(pose.transformBy(APRILTAG_RIGHT_TRANSFORM));  
}
